tiert kompatiblen Produkten auch unschlagbare Set-Preise und Nachlässe. Die intuitive GUI für individuelle Zusammenstellung und echten Mehrwert.[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image="1712" img_size="full"][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_pageable][hgr_counter icon_type="selector" icon="fa fa-long-arrow-right" counter_icon_size="20" counter_icon_color="#222222" counter_icon_position="icon-left" counter_number="1890" counter_number_color="#222222" counter_units="Lorem ipsum" counter_units_color="#222222" counter_text="" counter_text_color="#222222" counter_speed="2" counter_background_settings="none" counter_border_settings="none" counter_border_corner="0" extra_class=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1479825481193{background-color: #f2f2f2 !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_single_image image="1711" alignment="center" style="vc_box_circle"][vc_column_text]\n<h4 style="text-align: center; color: #000000;">Michael Stolte</h4>\n<p style="text-align: center; color: #0067b1;"><strong>Bereichsleiter E-Commerce</strong></p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1482329259066{margin-right: 50px !important;border-top-width: 3px !important;border-right-width: 3px !important;border-bottom-width: 3px !important;border-left-width: 3px !important;padding-top: 22px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;background-position: 0 0 !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;border-left-color: #ffffff !important;border-left-style: solid !important;border-right-color: #ffffff !important;border-right-style: solid !important;border-top-color: #ffffff !important;border-top-style: solid !important;border-bottom-color: #ffffff !important;border-bottom-style: solid !important;}"]\n<p style="font-weight: 600; color: #444444;">„Wir wachsen stark, erwirtschaften bereits heute 20% des Umsatzes online und das profitabel. Wir wollen immer besser werden und sind offen für neue Ideen und Wege. Die Flexibilität und Erfahrung von Mobizcorp ist dabei für uns von großem Wert."</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1480329749248{margin-bottom: 50px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/3"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][hgr_button hgr_buttontext="www.engelhorn.de" hgr_buttontextsize="16" hgr_buttonurl="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwww.engelhorn.de%2F||target:%20_blank|" hgr_buttontextcolor="#ffffff" hgr_buttontexthovercolor="#ffffff" hgr_buttoncolor="#0067b1" hgr_buttoncolorhover="#00529e" hgr_buttonwidth="346" hgr_buttonwidthunits="px" hgr_buttonheight="60" hgr_buttonheightunits="px" hgr_buttonborderweight="0" hgr_buttonbodercolor="" hgr_buttonbordercolorhover="" hgr_buttonroundness="30" hgr_hasicon="noicon" hgr_button_extraclass=""][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Engelhorn', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1702-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-12-21 17:00:29', '2016-12-21 16:00:29', '', 1702, 'http://localhost/preview/1702-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
